      <div class="msgContentFrame">- Ok, So i got my Shield when i was Rank 5-6 Glad..    I click Gaurd after initiating EVERY Fight... Tho i still only seem to gain around 25-50 SP for Shield every 2-3 fights sometimes get more when fighting Orange-Red mobs. Y so? <br /> <br />- So when m bored i will just sit after starting a fight,  Keep reactivating Gaurd and just heal myself.   I will rack up bout 150-200 Sheild skill points.  but that takes around 5-10 mins of sitting there -( just remember to attack once Every min or so to keep fight Active ).  is there a faster way to lvl Shield Skill?<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>Allana Sunfire <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1819822.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
